{
  "stem": "7598.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "She offered to sell it, but my father wouldn't.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Fortunately, he was very good at his job and he started-- again, in that business, you always seem to know someone.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And someone employed him originally for 5 pounds a week.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And there was a lot of movement in industrial diamonds because they were very important during the war.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And certainly my father started earning a, you know, a little money.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "About three months after we were back in Antwerp, we listened every day to Free Belgian Radio, which gave the name of the refugees who'd arrived in England.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "In fact, the Dutch radio did it, the French radio, [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And our neighbors or friends came and said they had heard the night before, the one we didn't hear, we didn't listen, that my parents were in England.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was a great relief.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] we couldn't believe that they would be in England.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we hadn't heard that they'd got killed, and they hadn't come back.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But the United States was not at war.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my father had a very good friend and colleague called Jack Content.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So my brother wrote a letter addressed to Jack Content, Diamond Company, New York-- we had no idea of an address whatsoever-- saying that he believes my father could possibly be-- our father could possibly be in England and could he send-- forward the letter to England.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This Jack Content forwarded the letter to Emil Rubinstein Diamond [INAUDIBLE], London.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And believe it or not, my father got it.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
